                    <strong>
                        How will our solution make a difference?
                    </strong>
                </p>

                <p>
                    To address this problem, Fourth Wave Foundation has been working with the Karnataka government on a program
                    named as “School Readiness Program - SRP”. This program runs from centers located in government selected locations
                    providing –
                    <ol>
                        <li>Physiotherapy and medical assistance to children with disabilities.</li>
                        <li>Coaching on skills needed to be self-sufficient and self-reliant for their day-to-day activities.</li>
                        <li>Training to be ready to join the regular school stream.</li>
                    </ol>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <u>
                        This program has been successful in increasing the enrolment of children with special needs in schools from 1% to 21%
                        (In approximately 3 years*).
                    </u>
                </p>

