                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Start a pilot of two Mini-School Readiness Program Centers (Mini SRP)- We intend to set up 2 Mini SRP centers
                            in rural Karnataka which will cater to the Children with special needs.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
